name: Christopher MM Backpack
description: The fruit of the House’s collaboration with Tyler, this Christopher MM backpack is made from Monogram Craggy canvas, with the Monogram reimagined as a hand-drawn pattern that includes terrier dogs and daisy flowers. In addition to a spacious interior with numerous pockets, there are two outside pockets for quick access to essentials.

name: Keepall Bandoulière 25 Bag
description: The uniquely distinctive design of the new Shearling Keepall 25 bag was inspired by the timeless style of vintage aviator jackets. A mix of shearling and cowhide is enhanced with a dark red leather trim and an eye-catching Louis Vuitton Malletier signature against a Monogram background. Practical and body-friendly, it is a stylish bag with a bold statement look.

name: Louis Buffalo
description: The new Louis Buffalo is a playful keepsake, clad in the Damier Buffalo with a red bandana in silk knotted around the neck. The cowboy spirit that inspired Men's Fall-Winter 2024 comes to life. This polished yet rugged figure features gold rivets as eyes and leather ears along with leather hands and tail in the Monogram Flower shape.

name: BABY MILO CAMO SHARK BE@RBRICK 100% & 400%
description:
Product: 0ZXFGM185906M
Manufacturer: CHINA
Material: 100% ABS

A BATHING APE®︎ ("BAPE®︎") and MEDICOM TOY have had a long-standing partnership, and through this collaboration, the two brands will introduce a new model, the BE@RBRICK BABY MILO® CAMO SHARK.
Based on the SHARK HOODIE, one of BAPE®︎'s signature items, the new model features a rare "BABY MILO®︎ CAMO" pattern, a charming representation of BAPE®︎'s CAMO. On the back are the initials "WGM" for "World Gone Mad" and BABY MILO®︎ peeking out of the SHARK's mouth.
The 100% (approx. 7 cm) and 400% (approx. 28 cm) sets are available in blue, green and pink, and come in a special "BABY MILO®︎ CAMO" box designed to match each color.

name: BAPE® X ASTON MARTIN GT3 118 MODEL CAR
description:
Product: 0ZXFGM185908K
Manufacturer: CHINA
Material: 100% ABS
Dimensions 24-30 cm

With the remarkable success of the Grand Prix’s showcase, BAPE® is proudly presenting Aston Martin GT3 1/18 Model Car Collaboration with POP RACE. The collaboration will give the Vantage a new look and keep it at the forefront of the action.
The overall color scheme of the sports car tends toward a bolder and trendier look by combining BAPE® signature ABC CAMO with the vehicle's personality.  With our mission to achieve perfection of product quality, the model car comes with a pristine acrylic case and a metal badge on the side. The 1/18 model car is not only the scaled version of the racing car, but a highly acclaimed collectible for your collection.

Care
• To remove dust or dirt, use a damp cloth or non-abrasive sponge with clean water. To care and clean any leather components, use a mild cleaning agent and a soft cloth to gently remove any surface dirt. Occasionally, it’s a good idea to treat the leather with a conventional, neutrally colored maintenance product. Avoid using any of the following, as they will damage your RIMOWA: scouring detergents, abrasive cloths or sponges, window cleaning agents, vinegar-based cleaners and disinfectants, solvents, dilutions and aggressive alcohols, petroleum distillates or nail polish remover.
• This product comes with RIMOWA's lifetime guarantee through RIMOWA stores.
